data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 1 story ranch in the Plantation neighborhood! Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. A lot of mature trees, this home has great curb appeal. Entering the home, you'll notice the large living room that opens up to the dining room. All 3 bedrooms are spacious and waiting for you to make them your own. This home is perfect for first time buyer.
